#: best-pkging-practices.dbk:1359
msgid "Some tools (e.g. <systemitem role=\"package\">po4a</systemitem>, <systemitem role=\"package\">poxml</systemitem>, or the <systemitem role=\"package\">translate-toolkit</systemitem>) are specialized in extracting the translatable material from different formats.  They produce PO files, a format quite common to translators, which permits to see what needs to be retranslated when the translated document is updated."
