#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n.dbk:110
msgid "To translate package descriptions or <systemitem role=\"package\">debconf</systemitem> templates, you have nothing to do; the DDTP infrastructure will dispatch the material to translate to volunteers with no need for interaction from your part."
