#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n.dbk:145
msgid "If the translator is unresponsive, you may ask for help on the corresponding l10n mailing list.  If everything fails, don't forget to put a warning in the translated document, stating that the translation is somehow outdated, and that the reader should refer to the original document if possible."
