#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para>
#: pkgs.dbk:837
msgid "Due to their sensitive nature, security-related bugs must be handled carefully.  The Debian Security Team exists to coordinate this activity, keeping track of outstanding security problems, helping maintainers with security problems or fixing them themselves, sending security advisories, and maintaining <literal>security.debian.org</literal>."
