#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para>
#: pkgs.dbk:1343
msgid "Further information relating to these and other package removal related topics may be found at <ulink url=\"http://wiki.debian.org/ftpmaster_Removals\"></ulink> and <ulink url=\"&url-debian-qa;howto-remove.html\"></ulink>."
