#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><para>
#: resources.dbk:841
msgid "The Incoming system is responsible for collecting updated packages and installing them in the Debian archive.  It consists of a set of directories and scripts that are installed on <literal>&ftp-master-host;</literal>."
